data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. PRICED TO SELL!!! Welcome to your oasis in the sought-after Eagle Pointe community of Groveland, Florida! This beautiful 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom pool home offers the perfect blend of functionality comfort and serenity.  As you enter, you'll be greeted by an open-concept dining room that seamlessly flows from the spacious living room into the kitchen, making it an ideal space for both family gatherings and entertaining friends. The kitchen boasts granite countertops, modern stainless steel appliances, ample cabinetry, a convenient center island, and a breakfast bar. The primary suite which is conveniently located on the first floor is a private retreat featuring an oversized bedroom, a custom-built walk-in closet, and an en-suite bathroom with dual sinks, a garden tub, and a separate shower. At the top of the stairs awaits a generously sized loft which is perfect for entertaining. The three additional bedrooms upstairs provide ample space for family members, guests, or a home office. The screened lanai which is adjoined to the pool is the perfect set up for refreshing swims and poolside relaxation year-round. This salt water custom built pool is only 2 years old and will serve you and your family plenty of enjoyment for years to come. Don't miss the opportunity to own this captivating 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom pool home in Eagle Pointe. Come and experience the Florida lifestyle at its finest ! Don't delay schedule your showing today!
